{"ID":"20260424101901-aty8upx","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-aty8upx","title":"06_编译器_图优化_后端生成","type":"doc","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-8dypo4g","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-8dypo4g","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"06 编译器、图优化、后端生成"}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-3ptqt7x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-3ptqt7x","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前两卷从硬件角度讲清了两条链："}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-80zj0at","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-80zj0at","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-pqwp1vx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-pqwp1vx","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-idoqwcl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-idoqwcl","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"数据复用 -\u0026gt; loop/tile -\u0026gt; buffer -\u0026gt; DMA -\u0026gt; 吞吐"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-ugjbxyt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-ugjbxyt","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-krtrmc4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-krtrmc4","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"少位宽 / 少非零 / 少中间结果 -\u0026gt; 少搬运 / 少存储 / 少无效计算"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-6e3z4xq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-6e3z4xq","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这一卷开始回答软件侧最关键的问题："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"这些硬件偏好怎么被稳定地翻译成真正可执行的计划"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​。没有编译器，模型只是一张计算图；没有后端生成，NPU 看到的只是“还没被拆成目标执行单元的意图”。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-hfu3j3h","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-hfu3j3h","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 为什么 NPU 比 CPU/GPU 更依赖编译器"}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-tvo0881","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-tvo0881","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"CPU 的通用性高，很多决定可以在运行时晚一点做；GPU 也有相对稳定的线程执行模型。NPU 不一样，它经常要求更早、更明确地知道："}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-ma8lytn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-ma8lytn","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-8iuxtu2","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-8iuxtu2","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-pa7igod","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-pa7igod","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"哪些算子能上 NPU"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-o4nr0lt","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-o4nr0lt","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-adm243q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-adm243q","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"tile 怎么切"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-gfoxsu6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-gfoxsu6","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-cvsqje5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-cvsqje5","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据流怎么选"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-joo5v0y","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-joo5v0y","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-xn236ei","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-xn236ei","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"buffer 怎么分配"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-jygpsfd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-jygpsfd","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-ebnldd5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-ebnldd5","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"哪些算子能融合"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-fp2ddby","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-fp2ddby","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-kakomru","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-kakomru","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"哪些部分要回退到 CPU 或别的加速器"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-3oqdn06","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-3oqdn06","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以 NPU 编译器的任务不是“把模型格式转一下”，而是把一张高层图拆成一组和硬件强相关的执行计划。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-d4b6pee","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-d4b6pee","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"真正的 NPU 软件栈里，编译器是连接下面两层的桥："}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-5scaxmo","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-5scaxmo","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-4mv6i2h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-4mv6i2h","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-rpcvfnp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-rpcvfnp","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上层：模型、框架、算子语义"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-aafu60c","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-aafu60c","updated":"20260424101901"},"Ch