ren":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"它适合做："}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-jgy497n","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-jgy497n","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-5b5lpct","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-5b5lpct","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-3kyh14g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-3kyh14g","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最终 codegen"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-r1clm55","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-r1clm55","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-4gc95wy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-4gc95wy","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"与驱动/runtime 的接口拼接"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-h0d0kza","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-h0d0kza","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"把 TVM 官方架构放进这三层会更具体。它把 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Model Constructor -\u0026gt; Relax/Relay -\u0026gt; Tensor Expression/TensorIR -\u0026gt; Target Translation -\u0026gt; runtime.Module -\u0026gt; Graph Executor / VM"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 组织成一条连续流水。上层 IR 保留图语义，中层 IR 暴露张量程序和调度空间，到了 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Target Translation"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 才分别把 host 侧代码交给 LLVM 等后端，把 device 侧 kernel 交给目标 codegen。这样再看“多级 IR”，它不是抽象上的层次美观，而是每往下一层就多引入一层硬件承诺。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-5i8zsqx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-5i8zsqx","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果跳过中间层，编译器要么看不懂高层语义，要么无法表达底层执行细节。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-gq4zfjs","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-gq4zfjs","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"多级 IR 到目标工件的连续流水"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/npu-study-06_multilevel_ir_pipeline.svg"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-52ufs0d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-52ufs0d","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这张图要回答的不是“层名怎么背”，而是每层到底多承诺了什么。真正排查 NPU 编译问题时，先定位自己卡在图语义、tile/调度，还是已经掉到 target/command 与 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"runtime.Module"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 的边界上。"}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-n0kh1ao","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-n0kh1ao","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4. 图优化不是“让图更漂亮”，而是让硬件更容易吃"}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-pen20n9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-pen20n9","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"NPU 图优化的核心目标只有两个："}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-ejg4fuk","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-ejg4fuk","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-7tkf7fx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-7tkf7fx","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-qxvpwka","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-qxvpwka","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"减少无意义的数据搬运"}]}]},{"ID":"20260424101901-56vbhyf","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-56vbhyf","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260424101901-g3n4bvj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260424101901-g3n4bvj","updated":"20260424101901"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"把计算重组